title: 11/04/21 DPS Hour 1 Tom Silverstein
itunes:title: 11/04/21 DPS Hour 1 Tom Silverstein
description:
Packers beat writer for the Milwaukee Sentinel Journal Tom Silverstein joins The Dan Patrick Show to talk about Aaron Rodgers and his positive COVID-19 diagnosis, with Tom thinking that the NFL may be "on the hook" for the situation as much as the Packers are.
